    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Jewish ritual pools used for immersion during various purification procedures and rituals. The Jewish code of law prescribes the requirements for the quantity and nature of ritually appropriate water  for ritual cleansing.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
